<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>LYon's Blog</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><description>Recent content on LYon's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><atom:link href="https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>打家劫舍</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%89%93%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%AB%E8%88%8D/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%89%93%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%AB%E8%88%8D/</guid><description>&lt;p>打家劫舍基本都可以用&lt;a href="https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%e5%b8%b8%e7%94%a8%e7%ae%97%e6%b3%95/%e5%8a%a8%e6%80%81%e8%a7%84%e5%88%92">动态规划&lt;/a>来解决。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="房屋偷盗">房屋偷盗&lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e6%88%bf%e5%b1%8b%e5%81%b7%e7%9b%97">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/Gu0c2T/">剑指 Offer II 089. 房屋偷盗&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="环形房屋偷盗">环形房屋偷盗&lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e7%8e%af%e5%bd%a2%e6%88%bf%e5%b1%8b%e5%81%b7%e7%9b%97">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/PzWKhm/">剑指 Offer II 090. 环形房屋偷盗&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>维护一个 helper，设定 number 的起始位置，自底向上计算两次，取最大值。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#e2e4e5;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">var&lt;/span> rob &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">function&lt;/span>(nums) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">if&lt;/span> (nums.length &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">===&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">0&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">if&lt;/span> (nums.length &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">===&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">1&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">return&lt;/span> nums[&lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">0&lt;/span>]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> result1 &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> helper(nums, &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">0&lt;/span>, nums.length &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">2&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> result2 &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> helper(nums, &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">1&lt;/span>, nums.length &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">1&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">Math&lt;/span>.max(result1, result2)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>};
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">var&lt;/span> helper &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">function&lt;/span>(nums, start, end) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> left &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> nums[start]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> right &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">if&lt;/span> (start &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">&amp;lt;&lt;/span> end) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> right &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">Math&lt;/span>.max(nums[start], nums[start&lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">+&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">1&lt;/span>])
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">for&lt;/span> (&lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> i &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> start&lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">+&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ff9f43">2&lt;/span>; i &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">&amp;lt;=&lt;/span> end; i&lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">++&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">let&lt;/span> temp &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> left
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> left &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> right
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> right &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">Math&lt;/span>.max(temp &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">+&lt;/span> nums[i], right)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff6ac1">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ff5c57">Math&lt;/span>.max(left, right)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="打家劫舍-iii">打家劫舍 III&lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e6%89%93%e5%ae%b6%e5%8a%ab%e8%88%8d-iii">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://cdn.yindongliang.com/2022/rob1-tree.jpg" alt="" />&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="kmp-算法">KMP 算法&lt;a class="anchor" href="#kmp-%e7%ae%97%e6%b3%95">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2></description></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%95%86%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%95%86%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%B1%89%E8%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E6%B1%89%E8%AF%BA%E5%A1%94%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E8%B5%AB%E5%A4%AB%E6%9B%BC%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E8%B5%AB%E5%A4%AB%E6%9B%BC%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%95%B0%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%95%B0%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</guid><description/></item><item><title>LRU 缓存淘汰算法</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/LRU-%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%B7%98%E6%B1%B0%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/LRU-%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%B7%98%E6%B1%B0%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>&lt;p>LRU Cache（Least Recently Used的缩写，即最近最少使用，它是一种 Cache 的替换算法）是一种常见的缓存淘汰算法。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>用于在有限的缓存空间中管理数据对象。LRU Cache 的核心思想是基于时间局部性原理，即最近被访问的数据在未来可能会被再次访问。Cache 的容量有限，因此当Cache的容量用完后，而又有新的内容需要添加进来时，就需要挑选并舍弃原有 的部分内容，从而腾出空间来放新内容。LRU Cache 的替换原则就是将最近最少使用的内容替换掉。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>